data.description: This versatile home makes life easy!  3 bedrooms, 2 baths, additional room off of open living space can accommodate an office/study, formal dining, exercise space, craft room, etc.  Kitchen is open to living room and has granite countertops, plenty of cabinet space and breakfast area.  Primary bedroom is located at the back of the home. It is spacious with walk-in closet and bath with shower, garden tub and double vanities.  Secondary bedrooms are split from primary, each has ceiling fan and ample closet space.  Main living spaces are tiled, carpet in bedrooms only.   Front yard is zero scaped for low maintenance.  Back covered patio extents living space- shades add additional privacy- wired for TV, ceiling fans in place.  Easy access to IH -10
